## Components Built

### `TextBoxSM` ŌĆö `src/components/TextBoxSM/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/TextBoxSM" ŌĆö single-line numeric/text input; 44px fixed height; ideal for price, payment, mileage entries
- **Props**: `label: string` (**required**), `modelValue?: string`, `prefix?: string` (left symbol, e.g. `$`), `suffix?: string` (right unit, e.g. `mi`), `name?: string`, `type?: string` (default `text`), `inputmode?: string`, `maxlength?: number`, `disabled?: boolean`, `error?: string`, `autocomplete?: string`
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [value: string]`
- **Anatomy**: 44px bordered box (`border-radius: 8px`, 2px border) ┬Ę optional prefix span (Neutral40) ┬Ę `<input>` flex-1 ┬Ę optional suffix span (Neutral40) ┬Ę floating label above ┬Ę error below
- **Border**: 2px `--color-neutral-85` default ŌåÆ `--color-accent-30` focused ŌåÆ `--color-warning-50` error
- **Label**: `position: absolute; top: -20px; left: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; color: --color-neutral-40`; `opacity: 0` in empty+unfocused state, `opacity: 1` when focused or has value
- **Placeholder**: `label` prop text, `--color-neutral-40` color ŌĆö acts as visual label inside when unfocused/empty
- **Input text**: 16px Roboto Regular `--color-neutral-0`, `text-align: right`; prefix/suffix always `--color-neutral-40`
- **Error**: `position: absolute; top: 48px; left: 0; font-size: 12px; --color-warning-50`
- **Disabled**: no "disabled filled" visual state ŌĆö disabled prop applies `opacity: --opacity-level-medium` to the control
- **Build notes**: Decimal commas auto-applied on 4/6-digit numbers (handled by consumer, not the component). 6-digit char max for numerics ŌĆö pass `maxlength="6"`.
- **Stories**: Default, Focused, Filled, WithPrefix, WithPrefixFilled, WithSuffix, DisabledFilled, WithError, AllStates, Interactive, NumericUseCases

