- **Light theme colors**: label grey=Neutral40 ŌåÆ float to Neutral70; value text Neutral0; line Neutral80; error `--color-warning-40` (#B30715)
- **Dark theme colors**: label/line Neutral85; value text white; focused line Accessibility80; error `#fa848e`; disabled hides the line entirely
- **Stories**: LightDefault, LightFilled, LightError, LightFilledError, LightDisabledFilled, DarkDefault, DarkFilled, DarkError, DarkDisabledFilled, AllStatesLight, AllStatesDark, WidthVariants, Interactive

